I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/signin/"
I enter "ma.zapataf@uniandes.edu.co" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "misomazf88" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/pages"
I navigate to page "http://localhost:2368/ghost/#/editor/page"
I enter "$name_3" into input field having css selector ".gh-editor-title.ember-text-area.gh-input.ember-view"
I enter "$email_2" into input field having css selector ".koenig-editor__editor.__mobiledoc-editor.__has-no-content"
I click on element having css selector ".ember-view.ember-basic-dropdown-trigger.gh-btn.gh-btn-outline.gh-publishmenu-trigger"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn.gh-btn-blue.gh-publishmenu-button.gh-btn-icon.ember-view"
